addiction-symptom-nausea-high-0 = You're on the verge of vomiting.
addiction-symptom-nausea-high-1 = You throw-up a little in your mouth.

addiction-symptom-headache-low-0 = This headache is terrible.
addiction-symptom-headache-low-1 = You have a headache.
addiction-symptom-headache-low-2 = This headache isn't going away.
addiction-symptom-headache-high-0 = Your headache pounds, and pounds.
addiction-symptom-headache-high-1 = This migraine is the worst.
addiction-symptom-headache-high-2 = Need something for this pounding headache.

